# Virtual Try-On Chrome Extension

A powerful Chrome extension that enables virtual clothing try-ons on any e-commerce website using AI technology.

## Features

- **Smart Product Detection**: Automatically detects clothing items on e-commerce websites
- **AI-Powered Try-On**: Uses Google Gemini AI to generate realistic virtual try-ons
- **Universal Compatibility**: Works on Amazon, Myntra, and other e-commerce sites
- **User Profile Management**: Complete profile setup with photo uploads
- **Rate Limiting**: Built-in usage limits with daily tracking
- **Secure Data Storage**: Supabase backend with proper security policies

## Installation

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Open Chrome and navigate to `chrome://extensions/`
3. Enable "Developer mode" in the top right
4. Click "Load unpacked" and select the extension folder
5. The extension icon will appear in your toolbar

## Setup

1. Click the extension icon to open the popup
2. Fill in your profile information:
   - Full name
   - Gender
   - Profile photo
   - Full body photo (required for try-on generation)
3. Save your profile

## Usage

1. Browse any clothing website (Amazon, Myntra, etc.)
2. Look for the "ðŸ‘• Try On" button on product images
3. Click the button to generate your virtual try-on
4. View results in the sliding sidebar
5. Save, share, or download your try-on results

## Technical Details

### Architecture
- **Manifest V3** Chrome Extension
- **Supabase** for data storage and user management
- **Google Gemini AI** for image generation
- **Content Scripts** for website integration
- **Service Worker** for background processing

### Security
- Row Level Security (RLS) enabled on all database tables
- Secure API key management
- CORS handling for cross-origin requests
- Input validation and sanitization

### Performance
- Smart image detection with size filtering
- Debounced overlay creation
- Intersection observer for efficient DOM monitoring
- Image compression before API calls

## Rate Limits

- 4 virtual try-on generations per day per user
- Usage tracking with visual indicators
- Automatic reset at midnight

## Browser Support

- Chrome 88+
- Chromium-based browsers (Edge, Brave, etc.)

## Privacy

- All user data is stored securely in Supabase
- Images are processed temporarily for AI generation
- No data is shared with third parties
- Users can delete their data at any time

